message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously crafted to meet the highest standards. It comes with a range of features designed to enhance your daily experience. Considering its quality and functionality, I would like to offer it to you for $95. I believe this price reflects the value it offers and I'm confident you'll find it worth every penny. Let me know what you think!
I'm interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $85. I believe that's a fair price considering the features and quality you mentioned.
